methods.nullCount:
Count the number of null elements in the outer-most layer of this column (i.e. does not count nested nulls inside of arrays)

:return: (int) the number of null elements -- 'useDeephavenNulls' counts are always 0 so that we may omit the validity buffer
methods.visitBuffers:
Append the buffer boundaries to the flatbuffer payload via the supplied listener.

:param listener: (io.deephaven.db.backplane.barrage.chunk.ChunkInputStreamGenerator.BufferListener) - the listener to notify for each sub-buffer in this payload
methods.visitFieldNodes:
Append the field nde to the flatbuffer payload via the supplied listener.

:param listener: (io.deephaven.db.backplane.barrage.chunk.ChunkInputStreamGenerator.FieldNodeListener) - the listener to notify for each logical field node in this payload
